-- Train, Bus Collide in Ukraine Killing at Least 37 People, RIA Novosti Says
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2010-10-12T07:54:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/train-bus-collide-in-ukraine-killing-at-least-37-people-ria-novosti-says.html
A train collided with a bus in
Ukraine, killing at least 37 people, RIA Novosti reported,
citing local law enforcement officials it didn’t identify.  The state-run Russian news service didn’t provide any other
details of the event immediately.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
